name: Mike Cooper
description: I don’t really have much to say about myself as they say a picture is worth a thousands words. I believe the more we get to know each other the more closer we become. I am a shy girl but warm up quickly. I enjoy outdoors and indoors activities but most especially am always busy due to the nature of my work. I am a very easy going, energetic, soft spoken, honest and compassionate, faithful and above all God fearing woman. I am only looking for a man with a noble charisma, someone who is willing to share their life and devote time to me. I don’t believe in been rude or mean and i tend to be friend with everybody.
